Mx%=8191
Dim Flags!(Mx%)
Print "10 iterations"
T=Timer
For M%=1 To 10
  Count%=0
  Arrayfill Flags!(),True
  Print "Iteration ";M%
  For I%=1 To Mx%
    If Flags!(I%) Then
      Prime%=I%
      Add Prime%,I%
      Add Prime%,3
      K%=I%
      Add K%,Prime%
      For K%=I% To Mx% Step Prime%
        Flags!(K%)=False
      Next K%
      Inc Count%
    Endif
  Next I%
Next M%
Print Count%;" primes",""
Print (Timer-T)/200;" seconds"
End
